{"title":"春妮子","authors":["梁拉成"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":3,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春妮子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁拉成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月临过年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天近一天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灶里火苗嗤嗤笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑得春妮羞红脸——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一桩亲事碰了心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜悦难遮掩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柱柱一旁来逗趣儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春妮白了他一眼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手头营生一世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁有闲心思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟你磨嘴片！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灶里火苗子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拌着笑语燃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没等春妮揭开锅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满屋枣糕味儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲出门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑出院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘到山那边……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}